title: NOW WHAT? We Got Ed's LJ20 That Was Stuck 40 Years In The Sierra Nevada Mountains.
author: Fab Rats
description:
#fabrats #mattsoffroadrecovery #thegoldennugget 
Today Ed's Golden Nugget rolls into our shop! It was stuck in the Sierra Nevada Mountains for over 40 years! Follow along as Paul makes this abandoned ride into the ultimate Resto/Mod for Ed from Matt's Off Road Recovery!
Make sure to follow along with us as we build and fabricate cool stuff!!
